《'''哈芬登郵報'''》（{{lang-en|'''Huffpost'''}}，原名{{lang-en|'''The Huffington Post'''}}）是一個[[美國|美國]]的[[多語言|多語言]][[網路媒體公司|網路傳媒]]。該傳媒由[[阿里安娜·哈芬登|阿里安娜·哈芬登]]、{{Link-en|肯尼斯·勒利爾|Kenneth Lerer}}、[[安德魯·布萊巴特|安德魯·布萊巴特]]及{{Link-en|喬那・裴瑞帝|Jonah Peretti}}創辦，並以新聞報導及其評論平台之形式開始運作於2005年5月9日。其立場被認為是[[左派|左派]][[社會自由主義|社會自由主義]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/1192975/The-Huffington-Post|title=The Huffington Post|work=[[Encyclopædia_Britannica|Encyclopædia Britannica Online]]|accessdate=9. Oktober 2013|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504194244/http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/1192975/The-Huffington-Post|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自從被[[美國線上|美國線上]]於2011年2月收購之後，阿里安娜·赫芬顿成為赫芬顿邮报傳媒集團之主席及總編輯；<ref>{{Internetquelle|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/07/business/media/07aol.html|titel=Betting on News, AOL Is Buying the Huffington Post|autor=Jeremy W. Peters, Verne G. Kopyteff|datum=7. Februar 2011|sprache=en|zugriff=2012-04-17}} {{Wayback|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/07/business/media/07aol.html |date=20210516033339 }}</ref><ref>Interview mit Arianna Huffington im Schweizer ''[[Tages-Anzeiger|Tages-Anzeiger]]'' vom 30. September 2014 anlässlich eines Besuchs in Berlin</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.voanews.com/chinese/news/20110207-US-AOL-HUFFINGTON-115462634.html|title=美国之音中文网|newspaper=美国之音|accessdate=2017-03-08|language=zh}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001037001|title=新聞人物：《赫芬頓郵報》創始人赫芬頓|newspaper=FT中文網|accessdate=2017-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210312052019/http://big5.ftchinese.com/story/001037001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/40587/BN-2016-08-12-032743-81|title=不要過度勞累取得世俗的成功！赫芬頓郵報創辦人宣佈離開公司，投入健康新創事業|last=楊|first=晨新|date=2016-08-12|work=|newspaper=數位時代|accessdate=2017-03-08|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516033356/https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/40587/BN-2016-08-12-032743-81|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，赫芬顿邮报之[[網站流量|網站流量]]一度超越《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》網站。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://digiday.com/careers/huffington-posts-midlife-crisis/|title=The Huffington Post's midlife crisis - Digiday|date=2016-08-15|newspaper=Digiday|accessdate=2017-03-08|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815140208/https://digiday.com/careers/huffington-posts-midlife-crisis/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/business/archive/2011/06/huffington-post-passes-new-york-times-traffic/351611/|title=The Huffington Post Passes The New York Times in Traffic|last=Estes|first=Adam Clark|newspaper=The Atlantic|accessdate=2017-03-08|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516033403/https://www.theatlantic.com/business/archive/2011/06/huffington-post-passes-new-york-times-traffic/351611/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年，赫芬顿邮报成為第一個獲得[[普利策奖|普立策獎]]的[[商业|商業性]]網路傳媒。<ref>{{Internetquelle|url=http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20120416/MEDIA_ENTERTAINMENT/120419908|titel=Digital Media Takes Home a Pulitzer|autor=Matthew Flamm|werk=Crain’s New York Business|datum=16. April 2012|sprache=en|zugriff=17. April 2012}} {{Wayback|url=http://www.crainsnewyork.com/article/20120416/MEDIA_ENTERTAINMENT/120419908 |date=20120602163829 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/36322/BN-2015-05-20-234111-77|title=《赫芬頓郵報》創辦人阿瑞安娜：睡多一點，談論成功會更加有意思|accessdate=2017-03-08|author=盧諭緯|date=2015-05-20|work=數位時代|publisher=|archive-date=2021-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516033418/https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/36322/BN-2015-05-20-234111-77|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年8月11日，阿里安娜·哈芬登因過度疲勞等緣由宣布辭職並表示將另創事業。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1512640|title=写完《茁壮成长》和《睡眠革命》，赫芬顿邮报主编就辞职了|accessdate=2017-03-08|author=譚方婷|date=|work=www.thepaper.cn|publisher=澎湃新聞|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420155801/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1512640|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5078332|title=連《赫芬頓郵報》都老了　數位媒體的現代啓示錄|last=黃哲斌|first=|date=2016-09-13|work=|newspaper=天下雜誌|accessdate=2017-03-08|language=zh-TW|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609160450/https://www.cw.com.tw/article/article.action?id=5078332|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0" />

2020年11月，[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed Inc.]]以股票交易方式收购[[威訊媒體|Verizon Media]]的赫芬顿邮报。<ref>{{Cite news|title=BuzzFeed to Acquire HuffPost in Stock Deal With Verizon Media|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/buzzfeed-to-acquire-huffpost-in-stock-deal-with-verizon-media-11605808800|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|date=2020-11-19|accessdate=2020-12-21|issn=0099-9660|language=en-US|first=Benjamin Mullin and Keach|last=Hagey|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119235745/https://www.wsj.com/articles/buzzfeed-to-acquire-huffpost-in-stock-deal-with-verizon-media-11605808800|dead-url=no}}</ref>

